title: Kanye West's Yeezy Season 5 Will Debut at New York Fashion Week
text:
| January 31, 2017 5:38 PM EST 
Kanye West photographed on Dec. 26, 2016. Clint Brewer/Splash News 0 0 
Kanye West ’s Yeezy Season 5 is set to show during New York Fashion Week, on Feb. 15. 
The multi-hyphenate will unveil his latest line in partnership with Adidas at Pier 59 Studios. And unlike Yeezy’s previously used locations (Madison Square Garden, Roosevelt Island ), it will be much easier to access, at NYFW’s frequented Chelsea Pier location. 
Read more: Watch: Helmut Lang Releases New Lo-Fi Campaign Video For Travis Scott Collection 
Yeezy Season 5 will be showing after Anna Sui -- a favorite of Madonna and Jack White -- and before New York designer Thom Browne’s 6 p.m. slot. The meticulous programming of Season 5 strays from West’s previous pop-up style runway shows, but will hopefully contain as many surprises. 
Billboard has reached out to Kanye's team for further comment.
